name: My name is help
description: Remember the image, rotate the whirlpool, the color of the rune depends on what level it affects, your consciousness should color the rune itself. It can be presented everywhere and nowhere, most effectively inside the body, your consciousness itself should tell you where ... When I was at the very bottom of despair, this rune violated all the laws of this reality and saved my life. Its application helps in any difficult situations. It provides the necessary wisdom and awareness in any sorrow. With diligent use, you will receive complete emotional relief and the very power of life, as well as acquire a completely new quality of personality.
